snippet.textDisplay:
May be my view is different from everyone. WRONG or RIGHT. I like both rahat fateh ali and abida perveen. But today after listening the first 2 minutes of the song i got to know........... Madam abida perveen can challenge rahat fateh ali or any singer with her microphone or amplifiers on standby. NO COMPARISONNNNNNNNNNNN... Today i got to know her ability n peak. oh my goddddd. Sorry if anyone dislike my comment. but i just spoke my heart. Abida perveen, ahmed jehanzeb, sajjad ali and Javed bashir .... Lords of Vocals.
Abida perveen since last 20-30 years never cared about her make up, cared to enhance physical appearance, SIMPLEST musician i know. Devoted.
